• Connect to like-minded people from the globe, embrace your community

Zynn the world, make it yours!

title: Zynn

creator: OWLII INC.
descriptionHtml:
Zynn is the ultimate short-form video-sharing platform. With Zynn you can discover new trends, create authentic content and share it with your friends. Our goal is to ignite your creativity with functions and tools to enhance your videos and support this fun-packed community. With Zynn you can be seen, be heard, and be YOU!

Advanced Algorithm: With our advanced machine learning technology, you'll be able to receive content from all walks of life, so you'll never be bored!

Creative Hub: You have unlimited access to all sorts of features, audio tracks and video editing tools on Zynn so you can create without all the pressure of editing, lighting and shooting. All you need to do is be yourself and Zynn will do the rest!

Social Community: On Zynn, you can engage with friends and even strangers with shared interests from around the world. Together, you can be creating, linking, sharing and Zynning!

We have some exciting new features to share with you!

Feature Highlights
[User Experience] The video watching experience has been upgraded to a high video resolution with a better interface. Enjoy high-quality videos in portrait-mode on your screens.

[Original Soundtracks] You can now create your own audio tracks to add to your videos! Not only so, you can save your tracks and share them with the community. Express yourself freely!

[Magic Effects] A new library of magic effects is added to Zynn and with these filters you can become a pop star or your spirit animal with a tap of your finger! Let's take your creative potential to the next level!

title: Zynn

creator: IMMERSITY TECH INC.
descriptionHtml:
Zynn is ​a short-form video platform that enables users to create and share unique videos with friends, family and beyond​. ​Zynn is dedicated to establishing a platform that inspires creativity and authenticity, as well as promoting and celebrating diversity, inclusion and equality.

With Zynn, you can enjoy:
🔸 AN INFINITE VIDEO FEED
You can access our endless stream of exclusive free videos that are customized to your preferences!
🔸 EXCLUSIVE MUSIC
You can use the hottest music from top artists or create your original soundtracks for your videos!
🔸 VIDEO EFFECTS
Take your videos to the next level with countless filters and fun effects! Edit text & emojis directly on your videos.
🔸 DISCOVER & SHARE
Have fun and discover new ideas with our diverse community of creators. Connect with people from around the world and make new friends!

Here at Zynn, we always strive to improve our user experience and bring new and exciting features with every update.

Feature Highlights:
◾ HASHTAGS
Want to make your videos easily discoverable on Zynn and more likely to go trending? Time to add your hashtags!
◾️ ORIGINAL SOUNDTRACKS
You can now add original audio tracks to your videos! You can also save your tracks and share them with the Zynn community.
◾ MAGIC EFFECTS
A new library of magic effects has been added to Zynn. With these filters, you can become a pop star or your spirit animal with the tap of your finger!
◾ SEARCH
Now you can find your favorite users and videos by searching their usernames or video tags.


With Zynn, you can be seen, be heard and be YOU!

Download now and join us on Zynn!

Have any feedback? Write to us at support@zynnvideo.com!

Zynn offers two feed modes of double feeds and single feed for you to fully enjoy a large variety of videos about sports and fitness, beauty, fashion, lifestyle, food, gaming, pets, vehicles, comedy and many other categories.

☆ Express yourself with creative effects Unlock tons of filters, effects, and AR objects to make your videos to a higher level ☆ Find lifestyle inspiration & explore millions of ideas on Zynn With lots of creators and users sharing lifestyle tips and creative ideas everyday, you will easily get inspired by new ideas.
